He has inspired Millions and touched so many Hearts around the World and Carries an Amazing Aura and was blessed to feel that today !!!

He along with his wife Anjali Tendulkar and Son and cricketer  of Mumbai Indians Arjun Tendulkar to Take Darshan from Ganpati Bappa at G.S.B. SEVA MANDAL, King Circle, Mumbai.
